title: Dell PowerVault ME5: Temperature Sensors
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors the temperature sensors of a Dell PowerVault ME5 system (controller,
 ASIC, capacitor pack and enclosure sensors).

 The check registers against the built-in Checkmk "Temperature" ruleset, so the
 standard temperature levels, trend computation and unit display apply
 (default upper levels 60/70 degrees Celsius).

item:
 The sensor durable id (for example {"sensor_temp_ctrl_B.1"}).

discovery:
 One service is created per temperature sensor that reports a reading.
